<template>
  <form @submit="handleLogOut">
    <input type="submit" class="btn-primary" value="Sign out">
  </form>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";

export default {
  name: "SignOutPage",
  methods : {
    async handleLogOut(){
      localStorage.clear()
      const response = await axios.post('ServletLogOut',null,{params :{ action : ''}})
      window.location.reload()
    },
  },
}
</script>
